♪I won't be a bird in the storm♪

164
00:09:32,627 --> 00:09:37,363
♪Nor sleep forever where shadows lie♪

165
00:09:37,651 --> 00:09:42,259
♪I only pray, in the decade to come♪

166
00:09:42,675 --> 00:09:45,662
♪I'll break from the dark♪

167
00:09:47,982 --> 00:09:50,003
♪Must learn the art of a silver tongue♪

168
00:09:50,195 --> 00:09:52,499
♪Must have a heart like a desert♪

169
00:09:52,982 --> 00:09:56,755
♪Only this stubborn flame inside stays♪

170
00:09:57,779 --> 00:09:59,891
♪Let the board be flipped♪

171
00:10:00,179 --> 00:10:02,622
♪The fate reversed♪

172
00:10:03,251 --> 00:10:07,187
♪Though happy endings won't come♪

173
00:10:07,635 --> 00:10:10,282
♪I'll stand with you♪

174
00:10:10,433 --> 00:10:12,822
♪Pierce through the flame of the night♪

175
00:10:12,943 --> 00:10:15,061
♪Even if the road is long and far♪

176
00:10:15,323 --> 00:10:17,282
♪Have no fear for the risk and danger♪

177
00:10:17,613 --> 00:10:20,110
♪When all the joys and sorrows♪

178
00:10:20,222 --> 00:10:22,821
♪When the dust settles, the music ends♪

179
